data.description: MLS# 270812, New Lower Price!!!  Welcome to your dream home in a quiet and secure gated community! This beautifully maintained 3 BR 2 BA rambler with bonus room greets friends and family alike with a welcoming covered front porch, slate tile entry, formal living room and a bright great room. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the stunning kitchen, where functionality meets aesthetics. Prepare meals with joy in a kitchen that offers an abundance of counter space, a convenient pantry, and a dedicated dining area, while the thoughtful inclusion of pull-out trash bins and custom pull-out cabinetry provides optimal organization. Discover the large master suite through French doors and enjoy the spaciousness of a walk-in closet and the privacy of a beautifully appointed 3/4 bath with walk-in shower and dual sink vanity.Seeking additional space for leisure or work? Ascend to the upper-level bonus room, a versatile area that can easily be transformed into a media room, home office, or creative studio! Embrace outdoor living with both a covered back deck and a covered front porch, perfect for sipping morning coffee or relishing in the quiet surroundings. The fully fenced backyard offers not only privacy, but space to add garden! Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property yours--schedule your private showing today!
